{"tid":987124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府引入中國殖民又拒絕大幅增加醫護職位，無非都係想引入中國醫護","createTime":"2019-01-19T05:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T04:26:49.000Z","uid":47359,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"823cdafd6e447d401d3ba7216b040cfb9cc6a618","tid":987124,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"之前都經黨媒/梁振英放過風<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.localpresshk.com/2015/10/cy-leung-welcome-china-nurse/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2015%2F10%2Fcy-leung-welcome-china-nurse%2F&d=G3JivrrVtvrQN9YN3IyjfpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=7d3c94e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.localpresshk.com/2015/10/cy-leung-welcome-china-nurse/</a><br />\n<br />\n梁振英認醫護人手不足　稱可研引入外來人手　早年曾提輸入廣東護士<br />\nBy 本土新聞 On 十月 22, 2015<br />\nShare this:<br />\nFacebookTwitterEmailGoogle+WhatsAppLineTelegramPinterestLinkedInWeChatVKRedditRediff MyPageSina Weibo分享<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nJOKER<br />\n圖：《蝙蝠俠》電影劇照<br />\n行政長官梁振英在立法會答問大會上，承認本港面對人口老化，醫療服務需求愈來愈大，有人手不足情況。對於會否引入外來人手，他說，若相關委員會檢視後，認為引入更多外來人手是解決辦法，會著手去做。他在二OO九年時任行政會議召集人時曾表示，若護士短缺，可研究從廣東省輸入。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n有千三名公立醫院醫生昨日手持「怒」字標語，在伊利沙伯醫院大堂靜坐抗議，不滿醫院管理局調整薪酬架構，未有跟隨公務員的機制，要求當局按慣常機制，加薪百分之三，並追溯至去年十月一日。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衛生局局長高永文、醫管局行政總裁梁柏賢等高官到場，高永文指，政府原則上同意醫管局動用本身的財政儲備為醫生加薪；梁柏賢則指示，在經過仔細的計算後，加薪百分之三的要求在財政上可行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n引進海外醫護人才 紓解人手不足之患<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2017/06/15/WW1706150001.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2FWW1706150001.htm&d=G3JivrrVtvrQN9YN3IyjfpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=ff6f3cd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2017/06/15/WW1706150001.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n解決醫護不足適當引入外援<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkcd.com/content/2017-06/15/content_1052690.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcd.com%2Fcontent%2F2017-06%2F15%2Fcontent_1052690.html&d=G3JivrrVtvrQN9YN3IyjfpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=1e0de70b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkcd.com/content/2017-06/15/content_1052690.html</a>"},{"pid":"f55974e2f9427499f29f1f550123c04ca7e52f9c","tid":987124,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:15:27.000Z","msg":"醫療改革都係為人民福祉著想 支持"},{"pid":"81621a82e982d2e1ac07022e53f8eb0512c18bce","tid":987124,"uid":47359,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:16:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">然後放一大班五毛放大啲醫療事故眨低香港醫療水平</span><br />\n<br />\n其實香港醫療水平名列前矛<br />\n<br />\n但醫護病人比例全球數一數二高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29384042597bb42bf4ba248daa868910919610b9","tid":987124,"uid":51469,"like":9,"dislike":10,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:18:53.000Z","msg":"狼又來了<br />\n<br />\n本文章由支持港獨的cmhk用戶關愛座hunter發出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df4d33e44412a8c84a2dde681e52a1f32d4e666","tid":987124,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:18:56.000Z","msg":"一早知啦"},{"pid":"cc7fe99d513d6dc3f7e2dfef41f3708a8af54caa","tid":987124,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:21:15.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"d4d761a742110cf122818a49e9fd3d086eaa11f2","tid":987124,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:24:35.000Z","msg":"[url][外國醫生唔想黎香港?]我地不如睇下以前幾多英聯邦醫生番黎香港執葉?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/cceKOS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/cceKOS</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]<br />\n等關囝反駁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0970c0fb97ec8911a2f18d711e79fbb0181d250c","tid":987124,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:28:01.000Z","msg":"關蛇用中移邊個plan 我用168 4g 10gb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4531c03f458421b78533ca699aa633b85cd5d7","tid":987124,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:30:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/154895/城市數據-香港需增2-46萬名醫生護士-始追上發達國家平均水平\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F154895%2F%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%9C%80%E5%A2%9E2-46%E8%90%AC%E5%90%8D%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%AD%B7%E5%A3%AB-%E5%A7%8B%E8%BF%BD%E4%B8%8A%E7%99%BC%E9%81%94%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3&d=G3JivrrVtvrQN9YN3IyjfpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=2dc0c79f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/154895/城市數據-香港需增2-46萬名醫生護士-始追上發達國家平均水平</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q1vjs6m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ1vjs6m.png&h=3a7f7a86&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q4Jdxx2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq4Jdxx2.png&h=cbd723c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NMxNBZH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNMxNBZH.png&h=7993efac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yRFb3EJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyRFb3EJ.png&h=7db6ee46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【城市數據】香港需增2.46萬名醫生護士　始追上發達國家平均水平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n社會新聞<br />\n<br />\n撰文：梁逸風<br />\n2018-01-31 07:00<br />\n最後更新日期：2018-01-31 13:46<br />\n流感高峰期重臨，公立醫院病床佔用率持續高企，醫護人手長期緊張。護士協會（護協）早前登廣告要求政府增加資源，增聘護士人手。<br />\n特首林鄭月娥最新（30日）宣布，即時撥款5億元予醫管局紓緩目前公立醫院服務緊張情況。<br />\n不過隨着本港人口老化，醫療系統壓力勢增，如香港需即時增加醫護人手跟發達國家水平看齊，還需多少人手？<br />\n截至2016年底，全港有5.2萬名護士，即每一千人有7.1位護士，比不少經濟合作與發展組織（OECD）國家低。根據2015年OECD排名計算，護士比例最高的國家是瑞士（17.9名）、其次是挪威（17.3名）、美國（11.3名）、英國（7.9名）等，香港的數字與立陶宛（7.7名）相若。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟發達國家看齊尚欠約1.3萬名護士<br />\n<br />\n經合組織國家的平均水平為每一千人有9名護士，若香港要即時追上平均水平，需要立即增聘1.3萬名護士才達標。<br />\n<br />\n以16年全港有5.2萬名護士中，有逾4成在醫管局任職推算，公立醫院需增聘逾6,500名護士，增幅佔現時公立醫院護士26%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本港每一千人只有1.9名醫生<br />\n<br />\n除護士工作量「爆煲」外，香港亦鬧「醫生荒」。分析醫生比例，現時本港每一千人就有1.9名醫生，比經合組織國家平均水平的每一千人有3.4名醫生低，數字與南韓（2.2名）和中國（1.8名）相若。<br />\n<br />\n護協歡迎林鄭向醫管局緊急撥款五億　促「貼地」紓緩護士工作<br />\n【冬季流感】護協質疑降低病床佔用率　梁智仁：絕對無「篤數」<br />\n護協斥前綫疲於奔命　批政府罔顧壓力　籲護士病人比例降至1:6<br />\n<br />\n若香港要從後趕上經合組織平均水平，推算現時還欠約1.1萬名醫生。2016年，全港醫生有44%人在公院服務；按此推算，醫管局需增聘4,808名醫生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n綜合計算，如本港要發力追近發達國家水平，推算欠2.46萬名醫生和護士，其中公營體系尚欠1.05萬人。讀者要留意，本文的推算假設公私營醫生比例不變，亦未考慮實際使用醫療服務人數等因素。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，港府去年曾公布醫護人手短缺推算，指2016年醫生欠285人，護士1,485人，數字與以上推算有一定距離。該報告推算，2030年時普通科護士缺人最嚴重共欠1,669人，最差情況估算更會欠2,727人；而屆時全港將欠缺超過1,007名醫生。"},{"pid":"57f36c161c28c481512eed105eaf571abcc2ea11","tid":987124,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0df4d33e44412a8c84a2dde681e52a1f32d4e666","tid":987124,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:18:56.000Z","msg":"一早知啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:35:43.000Z","msg":"但近排冇人提"},{"pid":"dc56db161d01662672eec3e2808d0636d56b4bf7","tid":987124,"uid":47359,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"d4d761a742110cf122818a49e9fd3d086eaa11f2","tid":987124,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:24:35.000Z","msg":"[url][外國醫生唔想黎香港?]我地不如睇下以前幾多英聯邦醫生番黎香港執葉?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/cceKOS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/cceKOS</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]<br />\n等關囝反駁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:38:31.000Z","msg":"呀五毛<br />\n人哋醫藥分家<br />\n我哋斷症開藥都係醫生做<br />\n所以個問題係搞醫藥分家<br />\n而唔係降低執業試等中國醫生都考到呀柒頭"},{"pid":"3ae40b3b17b20d3825248b8a988dbeb1fbe205b7","tid":98712